{"tid":1156508,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【慎入】【復仇者聯盟4】狂迷花7年時間變紅骷髏 :「從小就很仰慕他！」","createTime":"2019-05-15T15:54:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T16:51:31.000Z","uid":66923,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4a48047b6c52b6f7abbfce1388e6a26e5e34e8b5","tid":1156508,"uid":66923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T15:54:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2800356/org/3452555bfad431396761b8d155a0c467.jpg/zWNiuJZYDPIiCyeRXKuUeTpxb2YoPEL-2ZOFEtmThRI?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2800356%2Forg%2F3452555bfad431396761b8d155a0c467.jpg%2FzWNiuJZYDPIiCyeRXKuUeTpxb2YoPEL-2ZOFEtmThRI%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=b01c571b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《復仇者聯盟4：終局之戰》（Avengers: Endgame）熱潮席捲全球，不少影迷都喜歡扮演Marvel超級英雄角色；然而遠在委內瑞拉，有一名男子透過整形手術，把自己的樣貌變成跟美國隊長的死敵紅骷髏一樣。<br />\n<br />\n至於為何他千挑萬選，最終揀選成為紅骷髏。據了解，從小已經是漫畫迷的他，特別鐘情紅骷髏，所以他希望透過手術能變成跟偶像一模一樣，原來一切都是出自一份真愛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2800422/org/71e87aec38b469365ebb899c187bcc7e.jpeg/4M3vXvhQdpNK--Jzb6YU78ILL7zbl9aC9AemA_QHpgM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2800422%2Forg%2F71e87aec38b469365ebb899c187bcc7e.jpeg%2F4M3vXvhQdpNK--Jzb6YU78ILL7zbl9aC9AemA_QHpgM%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=9f4dbbf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紅骷髏在《美國隊長：復仇者先鋒》出現後，相隔7年後再在《復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰》登場。（《復仇者聯盟3》劇照）<br />\n<br />\n這位紅骷髏狂迷是現年40歲、來自委內瑞拉的Henry Rodriguez。據英國《每日郵報》（Daily Mail）指出，他在30歲時立定決心要變成紅骷髏，最終他花了7年時間，約30,000英鎊（約30.5萬港元），完成一系列的整形手術，當中包括削鼻、紋眼球、前額植入矽膠、剪開舌頭及面部染紅等手術。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2800479/org/a0fa10af61d3ef1732f10f60eabaafdf.jpg/zoIMeSAsPhlYme3wGCTzWBGjeQO-8ccn-Zw8afmcPGk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2800479%2Forg%2Fa0fa10af61d3ef1732f10f60eabaafdf.jpg%2FzoIMeSAsPhlYme3wGCTzWBGjeQO-8ccn-Zw8afmcPGk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=43885cf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHugo Weaving在《美國隊長：復仇者先鋒》飾演紅骷髏。（《美國隊長：復仇者先鋒》劇照<br />\n<br />\n紅骷髏首次出現在Marvel電影宇宙是2011年上映的《美國隊長：復仇者先鋒》（Captain America: The First Avenger），當時由Hugo Weaving飾演。相隔7年後，紅骷髏換上Ross Marquand飾演，影迷在《復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰》（Avengers: Infinity War）再見到他，當時他在Vormir星球，負責為尋找靈魂寶石的人指引路線。而今年的《復仇者聯盟4：終局之戰》（Avengers: Endgame）都見到紅骷髏的蹤影。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2800480/org/d2f5c36a5f1731e479e8dcb96847d410.jpg/uATAiVw7U1TqFvXzb4Hfif_uGoY_2J30Tl3W9k5d1vY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2800480%2Forg%2Fd2f5c36a5f1731e479e8dcb96847d410.jpg%2FuATAiVw7U1TqFvXzb4Hfif_uGoY_2J30Tl3W9k5d1vY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=42b65a7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在《復仇者聯盟3》及《復仇者聯盟4》時，紅骷髏變成由Ross Marquand飾演。（劇照）<br />\n<br />\n慎入......<br />\n'<br />\n'<br />\n'<br />\n'<br />\n'<br />\n'<br />\n'<br />\n'<br />\n'<br />\n'<br />\n'<br />\n'<br />\n'<br />\n'<br />\n'<br />\n'<br />\n'<br />\n'<br />\n'<br />\n'<br />\n'<br />\n狂迷Henry Rodriguez 花30,000英鎊變兒時偶像紅骷髏<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2800543/org/061e897b4fc47bdc5dc13729b3259725.jpg/FHri4nFS-M9vlDkiS21tqRhl2sZBuij2p4xlx6eMZcc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2800543%2Forg%2F061e897b4fc47bdc5dc13729b3259725.jpg%2FFHri4nFS-M9vlDkiS21tqRhl2sZBuij2p4xlx6eMZcc&h=202255ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2800545/org/7cea90216207c7f8c22a69c8f4078596.jpg/YSg_eTuVveJKj9QJTtoE-ubrnh06wtqc-J2hg_idoYM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2800545%2Forg%2F7cea90216207c7f8c22a69c8f4078596.jpg%2FYSg_eTuVveJKj9QJTtoE-ubrnh06wtqc-J2hg_idoYM&h=fa2030f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2800551/org/dd3b242c258e56273f7805921353a3b2.jpg/QskIgYrBY_AGC67bYpOf5EG4RMVhe5Uw5RS-XOUUvlw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2800551%2Forg%2Fdd3b242c258e56273f7805921353a3b2.jpg%2FQskIgYrBY_AGC67bYpOf5EG4RMVhe5Uw5RS-XOUUvlw&h=0da0cec7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2800556/org/2a3c706aace1c95451349a06398ebcbb.jpg/317H6gFqXt_rrv8_YhZcbx2n_A60s1MfxDz7XsQ8-14\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2800556%2Forg%2F2a3c706aace1c95451349a06398ebcbb.jpg%2F317H6gFqXt_rrv8_YhZcbx2n_A60s1MfxDz7XsQ8-14&h=13fe54d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2800557/org/df9414dfa7f856f1bfa3c2ad8f41de50.jpg/rEbRmeH3gBZTMmuTCriGbEAfc8-ShfqaRd3EtkXdxLY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2800557%2Forg%2Fdf9414dfa7f856f1bfa3c2ad8f41de50.jpg%2FrEbRmeH3gBZTMmuTCriGbEAfc8-ShfqaRd3EtkXdxLY&h=dea0111f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2800554/org/20478efa43d44f9665f25bc63d13e257.jpg/a3PPm6E4ipHfN0H2KqzjYAwszNrLwakyls_69ZbP-vU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2800554%2Forg%2F20478efa43d44f9665f25bc63d13e257.jpg%2Fa3PPm6E4ipHfN0H2KqzjYAwszNrLwakyls_69ZbP-vU&h=9da67b63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2800544/org/096af73224f283d42d19bca642ec2838.jpg/Bhn97feoVZRi0_Hy2KjHUn4AEcJQnCKTlAI7wJQCO8A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2800544%2Forg%2F096af73224f283d42d19bca642ec2838.jpg%2FBhn97feoVZRi0_Hy2KjHUn4AEcJQnCKTlAI7wJQCO8A&h=1f80e6c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2800558/org/2c63c034af128fbe73eefefc77d2ed8f.jpg/LrBBku_wcjEx59dG3k9wi_rLPrQmaVAFCs_jIQrP4yE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2800558%2Forg%2F2c63c034af128fbe73eefefc77d2ed8f.jpg%2FLrBBku_wcjEx59dG3k9wi_rLPrQmaVAFCs_jIQrP4yE&h=2237c227&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2800546/org/2e131b8e1301a95507ddf1bcf39f7d11.jpg/Nt-EglpCTMs4ABN-NoEKJtU_ur7GZ1Vk-vl0rPr5dKw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2800546%2Forg%2F2e131b8e1301a95507ddf1bcf39f7d11.jpg%2FNt-EglpCTMs4ABN-NoEKJtU_ur7GZ1Vk-vl0rPr5dKw&h=3b93dc18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wNztjys.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwNztjys.jpg&h=a5eb0fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHenry Rodriguez在2016年接受訪問時指出，他第一個手術是一項名為「inkeyeball」的紋眼球手術，之後在他的面部植入兩矽膠，這手術合共花了兩年時間：「先在前額植入矽膠、再在眉毛及臉頰植入矽膠。」然後把鼻子前端位置削去，再改變耳朵的形狀，最後把舌頭剪開，最終他花了合共130小時完成一系列手術，成為他夢寐以求的紅骷髏。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s61rQDD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs61rQDD.jpg&h=3591f287&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xz1GEwF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxz1GEwF.jpg&h=7f7fdc9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TqpQxRG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTqpQxRG.jpg&h=0b63b127&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cCSZrbH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcCSZrbH.jpg&h=0ee0cbcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4s5DGK2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4s5DGK2.jpg&h=eda89147&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHenry Rodriguez：「從小就很仰慕紅骷髏！」<br />\n<br />\nHenry Rodriguez續表示，他自小已經喜歡與眾不同，而且他是一個漫畫迷，並特別鐘情Marvel宇宙。他續指出自小便被紅骷髏的獨特外貌所吸引：「我總是被他獨特的輪廓，外向及獨一無二的個性所吸引。」於是，他在30歲時便展開成為紅骷髏這大計，並在37歲完成這個壯舉。「我想把自己變成這個令人驚艷的漫畫角色，這角色是我從小就很仰慕。」Henry Rodriguez指出。他坦言紅骷髏跟他本人的性格及態度有相似的地方。最後，他笑稱兩人唯一不同的地方是，紅骷髏擁有納粹意識形態，但他本人卻沒有。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pmsuOp3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpmsuOp3.jpg&h=beffdb6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CVu5mK3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCVu5mK3.jpg&h=5741d960&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nsv4Cip.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnsv4Cip.jpg&h=6f1f787d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X6ppCip.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX6ppCip.jpg&h=15059a4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5CxiGK5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5CxiGK5.jpg&h=9edfe0c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eQkwhiq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeQkwhiq.jpg&h=550fd66b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qjb0aDr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQjb0aDr.jpg&h=643b3068&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G8syvDr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG8syvDr.jpg&h=6c57d9e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然不少人認為Henry Rodriguez非常瘋狂，但他指出他其實來自一個非常傳統的家庭：「我想特別強調，我是來自一個非常謙虛及傳統的家庭。」他當時還提到要家人接受他這種生活方式確實不易，即使如此，但他仍然深愛他們，視他們為他的家人，據了解他已婚，並領養了一名男孩：「我的兒子Aar&oacute;n Rodrigo三歲了，如果他接受並愛我，我不關心其他人說什麼。對我來說，最重要的是快樂並接受自己，我們將永遠受到批評。」<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.do/eStKW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.do%2FeStKW&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2KxOsK%2BJamotDVaNSe1I1zI%3D&h=7b374fb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.do/eStKW</a><br />\n<br />\n好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a73ffb58ea7111c71cf9b5c3d397fc626bbb2084","tid":1156508,"uid":16635,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T15:55:40.000Z","msg":"marvel教壞細路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f372cb8361d9bb5efff9a048f879d5b6e4815c5","tid":1156508,"uid":183486,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T15:56:26.000Z","msg":"old news is...<br />\n<br />\n衰在使成幾十萬除咗顔色一d都唔似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd26e1e25e36fc6765feb00909b1e6f77aabc5e0","tid":1156508,"uid":43967,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T15:57:24.000Z","msg":"有冇心理醫生可以講解吓算唔算心理變態？偶像喺反派會唔會都想破壞社會？"},{"pid":"c4d12ace13e741f246f1bca6daa7d200cb63d932","tid":1156508,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T15:57:32.000Z","msg":"何必"},{"pid":"c316f5bfe350599045a3e5d8912963c023f55a7a","tid":1156508,"uid":47228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T16:04:16.000Z","msg":"紋眼球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ab276f0e404e24cfde7110f13bc5d95263cf4f","tid":1156508,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd26e1e25e36fc6765feb00909b1e6f77aabc5e0","tid":1156508,"uid":43967,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T15:57:24.000Z","msg":"有冇心理醫生可以講解吓算唔算心理變態？偶像喺反派會唔會都想破壞社會？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T16:22:55.000Z","msg":"會<br />\n所以唔俾人講nazi hilter"},{"pid":"765455b004ec2d8014bfbff7e0fade5df69e793c","tid":1156508,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T16:31:57.000Z","msg":